 [INSTALL NOTES:]
 ================

 1. Install program and open it
 2. Select HELP menu then ACTIVATE menu
 3. Now select ADVANCED menu then MANUAL menu
 4. Open Keymaker Core
 5. Copy "Installation ID" number from Nitro Pro into proper menu of Keymaker CORE
 6. Select "Activation" menu on keymaker CORE and one activation code is generated
 7. Select twice "Next" menu on Nitro Pro
 8. Now copy serial number and activation code from Keymaker CORE to Nitro pro and click ATIVATE
 9. Done
 10.Enjoy!
